'signature': True, 'channel': 'rent', 'description': 'This luxurious stunning apartment comprises 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom, plus 1 separate study room and 1 car space.
The apartment offers open plan living & dining, fully equipped kitchen that\'s wrapped in stone & glorious views to the city. There\'s your own secure car space & storage cage & direct access only steps away to trams, restaurants & hundreds of other local attractions.
With its private gardens, spectacular resident amenities & stunning near & distant views, "Parque" takes luxury living to all new heights. Featuring a 25-metre heated infinity pool, day beds, yoga area, gym & on the 11th floor "Club Level" includes dining space for entertaining, a library, barbeque terrace & business centre.

*** TO AVOID DISAPPOINTMENT, PLEASE REGISTER TO INSPECT PROPERTIES ****

Situated high up on the 50th floor, this near new two-bed two-bath apartment is perfect for anyone, making it the ideal lifestyle choice. Manhattan is a stone's throw from the modern Southern Cross Train Station, the iconic Flinders Street Train Station, Yarra River, and located right in the heart of Melbourne CBD.

The apartment offers a wide range of amenities such as:

- Directly opposite Southern Cross Station, with major shopping and supermarkets just around the corner
- Two spacious bedrooms with built-in robes
- Master bedroom with Ensuite
- Open plan kitchen with reconstituted stone bench top & mirrored glass splash-back
- Engineered timber floor, carpet to bedrooms and tiles to bathroom;
- Ceramic electric cooktop, stainless steel oven, range hood with ducted exhaust & dishwasher
- High speed optic fibre internet access, video intercom control, split system A/C
- Building facilities being an indoor pool, sauna and gym.
- Resident's access to the other joint facilities within the UWS development including, podium rooftop gardens, BBQ facilities, rock climbing facilities, 25m indoor heated pool and sauna, gymnasium, bocce fields, function room and study areas.
